                          ->  Seq Scan on rental r  (cost=0.00..318.72 rows=16472 width=8) (actual time=0.009..2.675 rows=16044 loops=1)
              ->  Hash  (cost=216.30..216.30 rows=4581 width=19) (actual time=3.666..3.666 rows=4581 loops=1)
                     Buckets: 32768  Batches: 1  Memory Usage: 492kB
                    ->  Hash Join  (cost=77.50..216.30 rows=4581 width=19) (actual time=0.713..2.562 rows=4581 loops=1)
                          Hash Cond: (i.film_id = f.film_id)
                          ->  Seq Scan on inventory i  (cost=0.00..75.81 rows=4581 width=8) (actual time=0.007..0.434 rows=4581 loops=1)
